# DevSecOps Tutorial

This project demonstrates the integration of security into the DevOps lifecycle using various tools and practices. The goal is to build, test, and deploy a secure web application.

## Technologies Used

- Node.js
- React
- Docker
- Kubernetes
- Jenkins
- SonarQube
- OWASP ZAP
- Snyk
- Prometheus & Grafana
- ELK Stacks

